title: iConnectYou

creator: Workplace Options
descriptionHtml:
"Access your Wellbeing Programme on the go! It's important for us that your experience is simple, convenient, secure and confidential. Connect with our specialists by phone, instant message, text message or video, anytime, anywhere. We're ready when you are!

Not ready to connect with us? Start by navigating through the app's robust emotional, physical and practical well-being resources on your own.
You need a passcode from your organisation to use this app. If you're not sure whether your organisation provides you with access to iConnectYou, please contact your HR team.
Our technology is compliant with HIPAA, GDPR, and various privacy regulations. For more information, please find our complete Privacy Policy at https://www.workplaceoptions.com/privacy-policy"
descriptionShort: Access your Wellbeing Programme on the go!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Thank you for using iConnectYou. In this release we are launching a new look and new features, such as the ability to share content, connect to social networks, and do more with your profile settings.
